 https://github.com/mixxxdj/mixxx/commit/830e864384ee1c96272997ee3f1dae4f71b28f3e,
 https://github.com/mixxxdj/mixxx/commit/c5b4368fd228feee28af4fb32ab6fbfd3f29f212
